<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. وَالْعِلْمُ إِنْ كَانَ أَقْوالاً بِلا عَمَلٍ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>فَلَيْتَ صَاحِبَةُ بِالْجَهْلِ مُنْغَمِرُ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يَا حَامِلَ الْعِلْمِ وَالْقُرْآنِ إِنَّ لَنَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَوْمًا تُضَمُّ بِهِ الْمَاضُونَ وَالأَخَرُ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>فَيَسْأَلُ اللهُ كُلاً عَنْ وَظِيفَتِهِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>فَلَيْتَ شِعْرِي بِمَاذَا مِنْهُ تَعْتَذِرُ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَمَا الْجَوَابُ إِذَا قَالَ الْعَلِيم إِذَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>قَالَ الرَّسُولُ أَوْ الصِّدِّيقُ أَوْ عُمَرُ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَالْكُلُّ يَأْتِيهِ مَغْلُولَ الْيَدَيْنِ فَمِنْ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>نَاجَ وَمِنْ هَالَكٍ قَدْ لَوَّحَتْ سَقَرُ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>فَجَدِّدُوا نِيَّةُ للهِ خَالِصَةً<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>قُومُوا فُرَادَى وَمَثْنَى وَاصْبِرُوا وَمُرُوا<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَنَاصِحُوا وَانْصَحُوا مَنْ وَلِيَ أَمْرَكُمُ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَالصَّفْوُ لا بُدَّ يَأْتِي بَعْدَهُ كَدَرُ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَاللهُ يَلْطُفُ فِي الدُّنْيَا بِنَا وَبِكُمْ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَيَوْمَ يَشْخَصُ مِنْ أَهْوَالِهِ الْبَصَرُ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>وَصَلِّ رَبِّ عَلَى الْمُخْتَارِ سَيِّدِنَا<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>شَفِيعِنَا يَوْمَ نَارِ الْكَرْبِ تَسْتَعِرُ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>مُحَمَّد خَيْرِ مَبْعُوثٍ وَشِيعَتِهِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَصَحْبِهِ مَا بَدَا مِنْ أُفْقِهِ قَمَرُ ... &gt;?<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>